esign）：学制1年，要求学生本科有城市设计专业相关的专业背景。申请截止日期为1月15日*(4)</li>	<li>建筑学博士（Ph.D in Architecture），申请截止日为12月31日，设有以下专业方向：	<ul>		<li>建筑史与文化（Architecture <a href="http://www.qianmu.org/历史" target="_blank">History</a> and Culture）</li>		<li>建筑技术与性能（Building Technology and Performance）</li>		<li>认知与组织绩效（Cognitive and Organizational Performance）</li>		<li>设计计算（Design Computation）</li>		<li>循证设计（Evidence Based Design）</li>		<li><a href="http://www.qianmu.org/工业设计" target="_blank">工业设计</a>（Industrial Design）</li>		<li>城市设计（Urban Design）*(5)</li>	</ul>	</li></ul><p>参考资料：</p><p>(1) <a href="http://www.qianmu.org/redirect?code=mrtw23K_LfWcHwJj000ryyy-L7iGj6Xtvm0m0gYBjrRsg_vuauodIU3jONQAknZGIUp" target="_blank">Architecture Program Information</a> Gatech</p><p>(2) <a href="http://www.qianmu.org/redirect?code=FrFYCW9oLzABIrghXBjM6TSoleE6LjEqgG_L0eB4q1lI7CDRDahZYru8wkSIvDm2WEs-1OBXPRbWwxOSdYKYgwunQkhFn-qfmiwFSEvqDiH" target="_blank">Master of Architecture Program Information (MArch) - Professional Program</a><a href="https://grad.gatech.edu/march" target="_blank"> </a>Gatech</p><p>(3)<a href="https://www.arch.gatech.edu/master-science-architecture" target="_blank"> </a><a href="http://www.qianmu.org/redirect?code=IrnDV7P3kCscvfDDIIIIIIGBCKnDLgv8fL3d3dy5hFDTxlgT20veM-TWZYaZfV1x2bna" target="_blank">Master Of Science in Architecture Program Information (MS) </a>Gatech</p><p>(4) <a href="https://grad.gatech.edu/ms-ud" target="_blank">Master Of Science in Urban Design Program Information (MSUD)</a> Gatech</p><p>(5) <a href="https://grad.gatech.edu/phd-arch" target="_blank">Architecture Ph.D. Program Information</a> Gatech</p><p>&nbsp;</p><h3>建筑工程</h3><p><strong>基本信息：</strong></p><table border="1" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0">	<tbody>		<tr>			<td style="width:83px">			<p>USNEWS排名</p>			</td>			<td style="width:66px">			<p>-</p>			</td>			<td style="width:85px">			<p>学费（/学期）</p>			</td>			<td style="width:132px">			<p>PhD：$15,582</p>			<p>MS ：$19,554</p>			</td>			<td style="width:85px">			<p>