ba/evening-program/admissions-application/index.html" target="_blank">Evening MBA Program Admissions &amp; Application</a> Gatech</p><p>(6)&nbsp;<a href="https://www.scheller.gatech.edu/degree-programs/mba/evening-program/curriculum/index.html" target="_blank">Evening MBA Program MBA Curriculum &amp; Courses</a> Gatech</p><p>(7)&nbsp;<a href="https://www.scheller.gatech.edu/degree-programs/mba/executive-mba/what-is-an-executive-mba.html" target="_blank">What is an Executive MBA?</a> Gatech</p><p>(8)&nbsp;<a href="https://www.scheller.gatech.edu/degree-programs/mba/full-time-program/admissions-application/class-profile.html" target="_blank">Class Profile: MBA Admission Statistics</a>&nbsp;Gatech</p><p>(9)&nbsp;<a href="https://www.scheller.gatech.edu/degree-programs/mba/full-time-program/curriculum/concentrations/index.html" target="_blank">MBA Concentrations</a>&nbsp;Gatech</p><p>(10)&nbsp;<a href="https://www.scheller.gatech.edu/degree-programs/mba/full-time-program/curriculum/immersive-tracks/index.html" target="_blank">Immersive Tracks in Leading Innovation</a> Gatech</p><p>&nbsp;</p><h3>PhD项目</h3><p><strong>基本信息：</strong></p><table border="1" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0">	<tbody>		<tr>			<td style="width:16.0%">			<p>USNEWS排名</p>			</td>			<td style="width:16.0%">			<p>29</p>			</td>			<td style="width:16.0%">			<p>学费（/学期）</p>			</td>			<td style="width:16.0%">			<p>$15,582</p>			</td>			<td style="width:19.96%">			<p>申请截止日期</p>			</td>			<td style="width:16.0%">			<p>1月6日</p>			</td>		</tr>		<tr>			<td style="width:16.0%">			<p>TOEFL要求</p>			</td>			<td style="width:16.0%">			<p>100</p>			</td>			<td style="width:16.0%">			<p>GPA要求</p>			</td>			<td style="width:16.0%">			<p>无</p>			</td>			<td style="width:19.96%">			<p>可申请学期</p>			</td>			<td style="width:16.0%">			<p>秋季</p>			</td>		</tr>		<tr>			<td style="width:16.0%">			<p>IELTS要求</p>			</td>			<td style="width:16.0%">			<p>不接受</p>			</td>			<td style="width:16.0%">			<p>GMAT要求</p>			</td>			<td style=